item.title: E-CTF - Misc - What Is This
item.description: Misc - whatisthis - writeup Description Intelligence has found same weird material from Mr. Codeshankar (yes,him again). So it is your task now to find out whats contained in it. The link is here Writeup after unpacking the zip file whatisthis.zip I get an image file whatisthis.png The file itself is broken and cannot be opened. After checking with the file command what that file actually is I am presented with the following: whatisthis.
